#. module: account_online_payment
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_online_payment/models/account_batch_payment.py:0
msgid ""
"\n"
"                This payment requires a KYC flow. As this process can take a "
"few days, please use SEPA XML export in the meantime.\n"
"                You will be notified once the KYC flow is completed and you "
"can proceed with the online payment.\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                Tämä maksu edellyttää KYC-prosessia (know your customer). "
"Koska se voi kestää muutaman päivän, käytä sillä välin SEPA XML -vientiä.\n"
"                Sinulle ilmoitetaan, kun KYC-prosessi on valmis ja voit "
"jatkaa verkkomaksua.\n"
"            "

